    • removeStudentRoster

      public void removeStudentRoster​(Student removeStudent)
      Deletes student from Binary Tree and roster hash table if student's ID and last name matches with any in Binary Tree, and if tree size is less than 20, dequeues from waiting list queue and inserts into Binary Tree - Average/best runtime is Θ(1), worst case runtime is Θ(n) for roster hash table
      Parameters:
      removeStudent - already-existing Student object
